# Installation Steps for SASS

1. Cloned the repository and created directory:
   $ mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   $ cd 0x03-sass_scss

2. Installed NVM (Node Version Manager):
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

3. Closed and reopened the terminal.

4. Installed Node.js version 20.16.0:
   $ nvm install 20.16.0
   $ nvm use 20.16.0

5. Installed the latest version of SASS using npm:
   $ npm install sass
